## Listing Annotations

> Example Request

```shell
curl <%=@api_prefix%>/2/annotations?start_date=2015-02-15&end_date=2015-02-21&location_id[]=7&location_id[]=8 \
 -H "W-Token: <%=@wiw_token%>"
```
```php
<?php
$wiw = new Wheniwork("<%=@wiw_token%>");
$result = $wiw->get("annotations",
    array(
        "start_date" => "2015-02-15",
        "end_date" => "2015-02-21",
        "location_id" => array(7,8)
    )
);
?>
```

